<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span><span style="color:#707070">[في الانكليزية]</span> Decision ،intention ،resolution volition<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
